text: Kardagushevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Kudashevsky Selsoviet, Tatyshlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 214 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 19 km from Verkhniye Tatyshly, 8 km from Verkhnekudashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tatyshlinsky District
title: Kardagushevo
